My point is, people talk about this like it's transcendental. I'm not even sure this artist has identified his artistic voice at this point. Mind you, I'm not calling him bad, I just don't think he's amazing either. FFS MELKOR MANCIN is Barry Windsor Smith-like in how he progressed from Sydney 1 to 3. I don't see what this comment section is seeing.
